A
2|Au\cdot v|\leq2|Au||v|\leq2||A||_{2}|u||v|\leq2\rho|u||v|\leq\rho^{\frac{1}{2}}(|u|^{2}+|v|^{2}).
2|Au\cdot v|=2\left|\sum\limits_{j=1}^{n}\rho_{j}u_{j}v_{j}\right|\leq2\rho(u\cdot v)\leq2\rho|u||v|\leq\rho^{\frac{1}{2}}(|u|^{2}+|v|^{2}),
|u|^{2}\leq u^{T}Au=\sum\limits_{j=1}^{n}u_{j}\rho_{j}u_{j}=\sum\limits_{j=1}^{n}\rho_{j}u_{j}^{2}\leq\rho|u|^{2}.
